name: Soup
description: Soups are liquid dishes typically made by boiling meat, fish, or vegetables in stock or water.

name: Salad
description: Salads are dishes consisting of a mixture of small pieces of food, usually vegetables.

name: Salmon
description: Salmon are the fish in a meal.

name: Dessert
description: Desserts are sweet dishes typically served at the end of a meal.

name: Bread
description: Breads are baked goods made from dough.

name: Pasta
description: Pasta is a type of food made from flour, water, and sometimes eggs.

name: Rice
description: Rice is a cereal grain that is the most important staple food for a large part of the world's human population.

name: Snack
description: Snacks are small portions of food eaten between meals.
